{"tid":1801174,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[多圖] 天水圍中學生集會 抗爭半年仍未放棄 你地呢？","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T13:15:47.000Z","uid":5780,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ce91658e386ab2b8336f123fa90c9ffd6d738713","tid":1801174,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"今晚天水圍14度，雖然唔係話好涷<br />\n但佢地抗爭半年，仍然為你地企出黎<br />\n由抗開始，天水圍同各區陸續都有大量人被捕、被毆打<ins><del><del></del></del></ins><br />\n當中天水圍最慘烈嘅一次、15歲郭同學頭中催淚彈昏迷一個月，好彩宜家終於醒番<br />\n<br />\n本應開心放假嘅暑假，為左香港走去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捱打</span></strong><br />\n可能係中學生唯一收入嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">零用錢</span></strong>，都用左去交通、買gear，會捱麵包、甚至skip一餐唔食飯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望你地可以繼續支持不顧一切為香港嘅中學生</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwfXPTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwfXPTU.jpg&h=bfeff5ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cf79a3ebe0cd82795f8f28e4e1bfc09ad9fa71a","tid":1801174,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><del>和你shop 升級：熱情香港 好客之道 又點少得你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</del></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7219e5ad5e71f5728220b9534dffc57500fc97d1","tid":1801174,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BgBW5s0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBgBW5s0.jpg&h=c90d5f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3bf7bc8ad80222cad4e36d4a7642fb41a13c4d0","tid":1801174,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"【工會戰線】杜耀明：小心防守大膽進攻，教協可扭轉香港人命運<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l